nodes.text: A Human male member of the Rebel Alliance, he served as a navigator aboard the Millennium Falcon during the Battle of Endor in 4 ABY.

During the entirety of the battle, he served in the freighter's cockpit alongside pilot Lando Calrissian and co-pilot Nien Nunb. Two other individuals - General Airen Cracken and Lieutenant Blount - were also in the cockpit during the battle's initial stages, before Cracken and Blount left the cockpit to man the quad turrets.
